 the nucleus of living cells. We\nfind that the selectivity of NTR uptake by FG domain films depends sensitively\non FG domain concentration, and that the interaction of NTRs with FG domains\nobstructs NTR movement only moderately. These observations contribute important\ninformation to better understand the mechanisms of selective NTR transport.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Apr 2020 11:09:03 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 4 Jun 2020 14:30:00 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-06-05"}
