olution and geometry. We identify a set of 37 jets that were\nrepeatedly present in best fits to several UVIS occultation observations. These\njets were probably active through the whole Cassini mission.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Apr 2020 13:32:42 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-04-07"}
