 more\ncandidates that can be found by enlarging the predictive samples beyond the\nstandard assumption of LRGs. In the future, we plan to apply our CNN to the\ndata from next-generation surveys such as the Large Synoptic Survey Telescope,\nEuclid, and the Chinese Space Station Optical Survey.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 6 Apr 2020 14:54:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 8 Apr 2020 03:37:20 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 17 Jun 2020 15:29:59 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-08-19"}
